    {
      "Channel": {
        "name": "competitive-AutomateFlow",
        "channelID": "ch-autf-cd5678"
      },
      "Message": {
        "User": {
          "userId": "eid_17be3111",
          "timestamp": "2026-04-05T10:15:00",
          "text": "I've been testing FlowMatic, a competitor product. Their webhook integration supports retry logic with exponential backoff, which is quite robust. However, their API rate limits are restrictive - only 100 requests per minute for the standard tier. The setup process requires manual configuration of each endpoint.",
          "utterranceID": "20260405-0-ddd01"
        },
        "Reactions": []
      },
      "ThreadReplies": [],
      "id": "20260405-0-ddd01"
    },
    {
      "Channel": {
        "name": "competitive-AutomateFlow",
        "channelID": "ch-autf-cd5678"
      },
      "Message": {
        "User": {
          "userId": "eid_27cd8130",
          "timestamp": "2026-04-05T11:30:00",
          "text": "About TaskPilot, a competitor product - their Salesforce connector offers bi-directional sync which is impressive. The data mapping interface allows custom field transformations. One weakness: their OAuth implementation doesn't support PKCE, which is a security concern for our enterprise clients.",
          "utterranceID": "20260405-1-ddd02"
        },
        "Reactions": []
      },
      "ThreadReplies": [],
      "id": "20260405-1-ddd02"
    },
    {
      "Channel": {
        "name": "competitive-AutomateFlow",
        "channelID": "ch-autf-cd5678"
      },
      "Message": {
        "User": {
          "userId": "eid_562b0f79",
          "timestamp": "2026-04-06T09:00:00",
          "text": "ZenAutomate, a competitor product, offers a no-code integration builder that supports drag-and-drop workflow creation. Their connector library covers 200+ services. The downside is their error handling is opaque - when an integration fails, the logs provide minimal debugging information. The monitoring dashboard lacks real-time alerts.",
          "utterranceID": "20260406-0-ddd03"
        },
        "Reactions": []
      },
      "ThreadReplies": [],
      "id": "20260406-0-ddd03"
    },
    {
      "Channel": {
        "name": "competitive-AutomateFlow",
        "channelID": "ch-autf-cd5678"
      },
      "Message": {
        "User": {
          "userId": "eid_571aa876",
          "timestamp": "2026-04-06T14:20:00",
          "text": "Comparing FlowMatic and TaskPilot - both competitor products have interesting approaches to workflow templates. FlowMatic offers pre-built templates for common CRM workflows, while TaskPilot allows community-shared templates. Neither supports version control for workflow definitions, which is a gap we could exploit.",
          "utterranceID": "20260406-1-ddd04"
        },
        "Reactions": []
      },
      "ThreadReplies": [],
      "id": "20260406-1-ddd04"
    },
    {
      "Channel": {
        "name": "competitive-AutomateFlow",
        "channelID": "ch-autf-cd5678"
      },
      "Message": {
        "User": {
          "userId": "eid_18c26797",
          "timestamp": "2026-04-05T15:00:00",
          "text": "Thanks for sharing these insights! Super helpful for our competitive positioning.",
          "utterranceID": "20260405-2-ddd05"
        },
        "Reactions": []
      },
      "ThreadReplies": [],
      "id": "20260405-2-ddd05"
    },
    {
      "Channel": {
        "name": "competitive-AutomateFlow",
        "channelID": "ch-autf-cd5678"
      },
      "Message": {
        "User": {
          "userId": "eid_d8f56413",
          "timestamp": "2026-04-06T10:00:00",
          "text": "Has anyone tried the FlowMatic demo? Can you share the link?",
          "utterranceID": "20260406-2-ddd06"
        },
        "Reactions": []
      },
      "ThreadReplies": [],
      "id": "20260406-2-ddd06"
    },
